data.description:
This 1 bed / 1.5 bath / 1,414 sqft townhome in the heart of San Diego's downtown Gaslamp District is a must-see! Features and amenities include:

-Location, location, location! Just minutes from the best restaurants, bars, entertainment, Petco Park, Trolley Station, and all that downtown San Diego has to offer 
-This 2-story loft only shares 1 wall with neighbors, making it one of the most private units in the building 
-Equipped with Smart Devices, including surround-sound home theatre system, Smart Home light fixtures, 2 wireless mesh routers, and voice command
-Condo comes with a 120" screen and projector 
-Chef's kitchen with granite countertops and Bosch stainless-steel appliances
-Luxury vinyl plank flooring in the main living area and plush carpet in the loft
-Office nook and built-in cabinetry in open-concept closet
-Black out shades for privacy and noise reduction
-In-unit washer/dryer
-Central AC and heat 
-Building amenities include gated entry, large fitness room, patio, recreation room, and nighttime security patrol
-1 garage parking spot and extra storage locker in garage
-Water, trash, and internet included. Tenant responsible for SDGE
-Small pets negotiable with additional security deposit
-Tenant required to have renter's insurance
-Lease term flexible, but prefer 12 months 

Available NOW. Rent $3,500mo. Deposit $3,700. Application fee $40.
